- Service Workers : https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API (annotated by Diigo extension)

- Use HTML5 <link rel="prefetch" href="..."> to prefetch (statically and dynamically) any type of data, for example: 
            const link = document.createElement('link');
            link.rel = 'prefetch';
            link.href = '/api/data';
            document.head.appendChild(link);

